keyAndDialogueList.dialogue:
This apron seems to be one 
of our only physical clues Abberline. 
We can start looking at some of the 
factory and dockworkers in the area, 
see whether they’d know anything 
about its origin.

The scissors are pretty damning. 
This does point us towards someone who 
would have considerable skill with these. 
Maybe a barber or butcher in the area?
